{"type": "article", "id": 15859, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2015-10-10T07:52:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 16954, "name": "Presek Design Studio"}, {"id": 16955, "name": "Palomar"}, {"id": 16956, "name": "Terry"}, {"id": 16957, "name": "NVy"}, {"id": 14602, "name": "Nick Wooster"}, {"id": 16958, "name": "Poggy"}, {"id": 16959, "name": "Charles Kalpakian"}, {"id": 15540, "name": "odo fioravanti"}, {"id": 16960, "name": "Carlos Jiménez"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 78, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122441hOxnbYQR6NBzkasZ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h3>\r\n\tWooden KOTLIC lamp by Presek Design Studio  \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这是来自塞尔维亚的设计事务所 Presek Design Studio 设计的灯饰，灵感源于塞尔维亚的传统中架锅用的三角架，灯就吊在架子中间，构成了悬空而对称的美。细长的木架简洁优雅，类似于衣架，富有生活气息。它还有一款是用亚光处理的钢材做的架子，也是相似的原理，更有金属感。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202633DqHNYrB7Ff4QaPmU.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74722222\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052026339dSuVn0N2eUmrZ4c.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.29166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202634GdvSU7eopqfXs9Qi.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202634o5mOnS28YX6GT1us.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.35\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202635guOJKev4oHXbNRQY.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.56166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tHorizons by Carlos Jiménez\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t玩积木和七巧板似乎是童年的事，这些木质积木能拼出假山和房屋建筑群的样子。来自西班牙的年轻设计师 Carlos Jiménez 从木工房的边角料里获得灵感，将经过细心计算的三角形和四边形组成了 12 块的套装积木，它们随意变化，搭建出小型景观，是改变办公室枯燥环境的点缀。在摆弄当中，也能舒缓压力。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202635qBX0gEVeF13WxhtC.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202636G64rClOqI5fgm3kS.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202636qon6WHrkhRUIbSiO.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202637jKFUZnzwOH9LvQgS.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202637bgBviyceOC5SaAUk.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\trocky by Charles Kalpakian \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t黎巴嫩设计师 Charles Kalpakian 酷爱玩弄错觉艺术，推出了一款名叫“rocky”的书柜，主要由长方形和菱形表面组成。从不同角度看过去，反光面都是不同的，使书柜呈现出不同的立体样式，令人对凹凸产生错觉，有未来感。部件全部通过 3D 打印制作，有蓝、黑、银灰三种颜色。<a href=\"http://www.lachance.fr/fr/product/details/16/Rocky\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202638z89vjAatWh51kfRF.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.08801956\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202638GfnsTXoej5Jhi93t.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.06356968\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202638yMtmEQZz8DNFTB0w.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202639w2UlAiuXefVpk3Km.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5599022\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202640gGPWmxo6SyhtcrM7.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.81418093\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tPalomar by Odo Fioravanti &amp; Palomar\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这是一款便携式的自行车车铃，来自米兰设计师 Odo Fioravanti 和意大利仪器品牌 Palomar。车铃另外配有一根带磁性的绑带，拴在自行车把上，就可以将车铃直接吸上去。取下车铃能直接揣在兜里，换另一辆自行车装上。按动车铃时，可以发出高达 80 分贝的声音，还能实现三种铃声都会循环播放。有黑、红、白三种颜色可选，售价 20 英镑。<a href=\"http://www.palomarweb.com/product/nello/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202641iKH06MISd78Lq4jm.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70415648\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202641CspSEkRi9nyFX3ql.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.79462103\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202642Qt5cYfbMkEuvGNqn.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.61124694\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202642FOpWdSnJTf3rMu0a.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.79462103\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202642AGO8zUcYWxej9Hbq.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.2591687\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202643Mk0vHLwV59YptSWP.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.27139364\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t家用电梯 by Terry Lifts\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这是一间家用的升降电梯，适合两层以上的住宅和腿脚不便的人。六角形的空间只能容纳有限的人，一旦超重就会停止运作，却也有不占用空间的优点。而四周透明的玻璃使电梯看上去像一个小型的电话亭，也给人一种安全感。靠墙的操控面可以选择不同颜色，以搭配不同风格的房间。制作方来自拥有 40 年电梯设计经验的英国设计团体 Terry Lifts，在防火等安全问题上都有可信赖的保障。<a href=\"http://www.terrylifts.co.uk/products/home-lifts/lifestyle-home-elevator-lift/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202644VM5CIo3BAvwpuK1H.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67692308\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202644DL5INX1UwaogO0ES.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.72307692\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202644oBvZxVtHz3nkN80d.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.64769231\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143144BnMPvqyfGcVNRxEw.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"401\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.61692308\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202645fo1GpJBvOxAUV6Fr.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.37314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052026465hVqPLRI2HrnpQ4w.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75324675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tNVy 秋冬包饰 by Nick Wooster &amp; Poggy \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\tNick Wooster 和日本时尚品牌 UNITED ARROWS &amp; SONS 的设计总监 Poggy 联合创办了一个新的品牌 NVy 。以”海军蓝“为主色调，结合了街头时尚与日式设计。自 9 月推出首个服饰系列之后又于近日推出了 8 件包饰单品。延续了深蓝色调和由  Komatsu Seiren Co. 加工的涤纶尼龙面料，十分耐用，整体呈现出硬朗的军事风格，适合秋冬季节和户外的场所。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052026468QjunlYSJgZ4UAOE.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202646kFpZLcVb2h31aGms.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052026479pwn1dO5vfJSR4bB.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202647glUfPM9wXSCsENDO.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202648SY6Wbw095JEmgHdj.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052026489sC7fEawB8iPz5VY.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202649eYCriyNfXoj5K6TE.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202649dlKuiQgYfWyAD1In.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}